{"tid":599886,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府擬向低薪無薪者派錢　人數百萬計","createTime":"2018-03-21T00:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T02:07:40.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ba553575e2fffe8758f65bde62314809dac6d0","tid":599886,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/081758_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F081758_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8d18f2cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n財政司司長陳茂波承諾透過關愛基金就《預算案》的受惠群組「補漏拾遺」後，包括新民黨、民主黨及工聯會在內的多個政黨，都向政府提出向低收入人士「派錢」的建議。報道指，據悉，為了達致「補漏拾遺」的效果，政府正積極考慮政黨建議，向《預算案》沒有得益的人士派發現金津貼，但金額及合資格劃線問題仍未決定。根據初步構思，政府傾向向十八歲以上收入較低及沒有收入的人士派發現金津貼，但領取綜援、低收入津貼及長者津貼的人士，由於已有「三糧」，所以不會有雙重得益。預料新措施的受惠人士數以百萬計。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/派錢補鑊-星島引消息-政府擬向低薪無薪者派錢-人數百萬計/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E8%A3%9C%E9%91%8A-%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E5%90%91%E4%BD%8E%E8%96%AA%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E8%80%85%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2-%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E8%A8%88%2F&d=qGvFEy8J0bndsSsVQd2qMZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=9b940166\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E8%A3%9C%E9%91%8A-%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E5%90%91%E4%BD%8E%E8%96%AA%E7%84%A1%E8%96%AA%E8%80%85%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2-%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E8%A8%88%2F&h=119c2c45\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/派錢補鑊-星島引消息-政府擬向低薪無薪者派錢-人數百萬計/</a>"},{"pid":"fb3f4bf6b375e8a4372d20ea696d6f38ed20334c","tid":599886,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8ba553575e2fffe8758f65bde62314809dac6d0","tid":599886,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s